      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            10Web: 70% Commission (Not for You)
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-4">
            10Web offers <strong class="text-white">70% recurring commission</strong> to affiliates. That's insane - double most competitors.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-4">
            <strong class="text-white">What this means:</strong> They're aggressively buying market share. For you, this means frequent promos, aggressive pricing, and premium features trickling down to free tiers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">
            <strong>The catch:</strong> WordPress ecosystem only. If you don't need WordPress integration, Framer or Durable serve you better.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">8.8<span class="text-xl text-gray-500">/10</span></div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Best for WordPress users who need AI + WooCommerce</p>
          <a href="/reviews/10web-ai" class="inline-block w-full text-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#10B981] text-white font-black hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors">
