          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- DEAL HUNTING MISTAKES -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 py-16 mb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2">Deal Hunting Mistakes I've Made</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 ml-4">Learn from my expensive failures</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border-l-[4px] border-[#10B981] p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-2">Mistake #1: Annual Subscriptions for Unproven Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-red-400">Cost me $348</strong> on a tool I abandoned after 3 months.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Always start with monthly billing. Most tools offer monthly - you just have to hunt for it buried in pricing. Only switch to annual after 3 months of daily use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border-l-[4px] border-emerald-500 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-2">Mistake #2: Ignoring Free Trial Limitations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-red-400">Wasted 12 hours</strong> building on Framer's free tier, hit export limit, couldn't migrate.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Check what "free" actually means BEFORE you start building. Can you export? Is there a storage limit? Does branding stick? I note these in every review.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border-l-[4px] border-teal-500 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-2">Mistake #3: Waiting for "Better Deals"</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-red-400">Lost 6 weeks</strong> waiting for a Black Friday promo that never came.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> AI website builders don't do traditional sales. Their promos are ongoing: free trials, commission-based affiliate offers, educational discounts. If you need it now, start with the free trial.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Deal Comparison</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-[3px] border-gray-300">
        <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-black">Tool</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-black">Free Trial</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-black">Best For</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-black">Rating</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {currentDeals.map(deal => (
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">{deal.tool}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">{deal.freeTrial ? '‚úì Yes' : '‚úó No'}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm">{deal.bestFor}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-black text-[#10B981]">{deal.rating}/10</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY DEALS EXPIRE -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-50 border-y-[3px] border-emerald-200 py-12 mb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Deals Expire (And How to Use That)</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[#10B981] text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Revenue Targets</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Promos end when they hit acquisition targets. Time your signup for end-of-quarter (March, June, Sept, Dec).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-600 text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Product Updates</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">New features often reset pricing cycles. Watch for feature launches - they're usually accompanied by promos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-teal-600 text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Competitive Pressure</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">When a competitor launches, existing tools often match with counter-offers. I track these and update deals immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

